[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +## 16. AI Learning Progress Review
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +├── components/
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +The AI Learning Progress Review feature generates a comprehensive, tutor-style report analyzing a user's study activity over a specified date range. It combines data aggregation from the Learning Journey Engine with AI-powered analysis via the AI Tutor pipeline.
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +│   └── ReportSection.tsx           # Shared section wrapper
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +│   ├── DateRangeSelector.tsx       # 7-day / 30-day / custom range picker
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +├── services/
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +│   └── useProgressReview.ts        # State management hook
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +├── index.ts                        # Public exports
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### Architecture
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +│   ├── progressReviewService.ts    # Data aggregation + AI orchestration
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +│   └── __tests__/                  # Unit tests
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +├── hooks/
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +│   ├── ProgressReviewPanel.tsx     # Main report UI (all sections)
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +packages/ai-tutor/
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +├── src/
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +packages/learning-engine/src/progress/
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +└── ProgressReviewPage.tsx          # Page wrapper
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +└── AIProgressReviewService.ts      # Server-side data aggregation (fallback)
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +Packages:
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +│   │   └── AIProgressReviewController.ts  # AI call + response parsing
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +│   ├── controllers/
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +│   └── prompts/
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +│       └── learningProgressReview.ts      # Prompt + response schema
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +```
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| Field | Type | Description |
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +The report is built from the `AIProgressReviewResponse` interface defined at `packages/ai-tutor/src/prompts/learningProgressReview.ts:78`:
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### Data Model
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `overallSummary` | `string` | Concise paragraph summarizing the learning period |
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +|-------|------|-------------|
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `improvements` | `string[]` | Specific skills or habits where the user improved |
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +Feature Module (apps/web/src/features/progressReview/)
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `repeatedMistakes` | `RepeatedMistake[]` | Mistake patterns with frequency and analysis |
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `vocabularyReviewStatus` | `VocabReviewStatus` | Total saved, mastered, still-learning counts + recommendation |
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr]  
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `skillProgress` | `SkillProgressItem[]` | Per-skill stats: sessions, accuracy, trend, analysis |
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `recommendedFocus` | `string[]` | 3-5 prioritized actions for the next period |
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `tutorFeedback` | `string` | Warm, personalized encouraging message |
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +Supporting input types (`ProgressReviewData`) include:
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +|-------|--------|-------------|
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `summary` | Aggregated sessions + tasks | Study stats (minutes, sessions, days active, streak) |
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| Input | Source | Description |
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `vocabularyStatus` | Vocabulary entries + reviews | New, learning, reviewing, mastered counts |
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `weaknessReport` | Mistakes + session data | Weak skills by severity, repeated mistake patterns |
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.507Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `studyPlanAdherence` | `string` | Evaluation of study consistency and plan adherence |
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `struggles` | `string[]` | Areas needing focused practice |
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `recommendations` | Generated by detection engine | Data-driven study suggestions |
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `tutorFeedback` | Generated by feedback engine | Encouraging message based on metrics |
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +The `DateRangeSelector` component (`apps/web/src/features/progressReview/components/DateRangeSelector.tsx:4`) offers three options:
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `skillProgress` | Reading/listening/writing/speaking sessions | Per-skill session count, accuracy, trend |
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +|--------|-------|-------------|
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `7d` | Last 7 days | Weekly review for short-term progress |
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### Date Range Presets
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `custom` | User-defined | Arbitrary start/end date via date inputs |
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### Data Flow
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| Preset | Range | Description |
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +```
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +User clicks "Generate Progress Report" → ProgressReviewPanel
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +User selects date range → DateRangeSelector
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +       ↓
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +useProgressReview hook → generateProgressReview service
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +       ↓
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +       ↓
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +│ 1. Query IndexedDB for all records in date range   │
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +│    (tasks, reading, listening, writing, speaking,  │
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +│                                                    │
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +│     vocabulary, vocab reviews, mistakes, progress) │
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +│               progressReviewService                │
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +│ 3. Check if AI is configured (API key present)     │
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `30d` | Last 30 days | Monthly review for broader trends |
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +│    ├─ Yes → build AI prompt → call AI → parse JSON │
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +│    │         └─ parse fails? → use fallback        │
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +│ 2. Compute local skill stats & fallback report     │
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +│                                                    │
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +ProgressReviewReport → ProgressReviewPanel (render)
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +│    └─ No  → return data-driven report directly     │
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +       ↓
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +│                                                    │
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Act as an experienced IELTS tutor
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +The AI prompt is constructed in `buildAiPrompt()` at `apps/web/src/features/progressReview/services/progressReviewService.ts:282`. It injects structured study data into a prompt that instructs the AI to behave as a personal IELTS tutor.
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +**System prompt** roles:
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Be specific, reference actual data
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +```
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Be honest but encouraging
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Write in warm, professional tutor tone with "you"
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Return valid JSON only
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Active days, total study time, session count, streak
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Study period with start/end dates
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Skill-by-skill progress table
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### AI Prompt Design
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +└────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Vocabulary status breakdown
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Unresolved mistakes with frequency
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +**User prompt** includes:
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +When the AI call fails (no API key, network error, unparseable response), the system falls back to `buildReportFromData()` at `apps/web/src/features/progressReview/services/progressReviewService.ts:157`. This generates a structured report using local computation:
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Recommendations from rule-based heuristics (weak skills, low consistency, unresolved mistakes)
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Skill trends computed from `ProgressRecord` comparisons
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Explicit instruction to cover all 9 report sections
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### Fallback Mechanism
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Vocabulary stats from review intervals and repetitions
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +The fallback always produces a valid `ProgressReviewReport` — the feature never shows an empty state after generation.
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### AI Provider Configuration
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Study consistency from session date arithmetic
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +Uses the same configuration as the AI Tutor (section 9). If the user has not configured an API key, the feature returns a data-driven report without attempting an AI call.
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| Component | File | Responsibility |
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.508Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.509Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### UI Components
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.509Z] [INFO] [stderr] +|-----------|------|----------------|
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.509Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `SkillProgressSection` | `components/ProgressReviewPanel.tsx` | Per-skill progress bars with accuracy and trend |
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.509Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `ProgressReviewPanel` | `components/ProgressReviewPanel.tsx` | Main layout, state management, all 9 report sections |
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.509Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `DateRangeSelector` | `components/DateRangeSelector.tsx` | Preset buttons + custom date inputs |
[2026-07-05T05:28:49.509Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `ReportSection` | `components/ReportSection.tsx` | Reusable section wrapper with icon and badge |
