[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +## 16. AI Learning Progress Review
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr]  All colors, spacing, typography, and shadows are defined as CSS custom properties in `packages/theme/src/tokens.css`.
