[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### Architecture
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +│   ├── DateRangeSelector.tsx       # 7-day / 30-day / custom range picker
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +The AI Learning Progress Review feature generates a comprehensive, tutor-style report analyzing a user's study activity over a specified date range. It combines data aggregation from the Learning Journey Engine with AI-powered analysis via the AI Tutor pipeline.
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +│   ├── ProgressReviewPanel.tsx     # Main report UI (all sections)
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +```
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +│   └── ReportSection.tsx           # Shared section wrapper
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +│   └── useProgressReview.ts        # State management hook
