[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### Data Model
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +│   ├── controllers/
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `improvements` | `string[]` | Specific skills or habits where the user improved |
