[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +|-------|------|-------------|
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `repeatedMistakes` | `RepeatedMistake[]` | Mistake patterns with frequency and analysis |
