[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `studyPlanAdherence` | `string` | Evaluation of study consistency and plan adherence |
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `tutorFeedback` | `string` | Warm, personalized encouraging message |
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `vocabularyReviewStatus` | `VocabReviewStatus` | Total saved, mastered, still-learning counts + recommendation |
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `overallSummary` | `string` | Concise paragraph summarizing the learning period |
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +Supporting input types (`ProgressReviewData`) include:
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| Input | Source | Description |
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `weaknessReport` | Mistakes + session data | Weak skills by severity, repeated mistake patterns |
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `skillProgress` | Reading/listening/writing/speaking sessions | Per-skill session count, accuracy, trend |
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `vocabularyStatus` | Vocabulary entries + reviews | New, learning, reviewing, mastered counts |
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `recommendations` | Generated by detection engine | Data-driven study suggestions |
