[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### Date Range Presets
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `summary` | Aggregated sessions + tasks | Study stats (minutes, sessions, days active, streak) |
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +|--------|-------|-------------|
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +The `DateRangeSelector` component (`apps/web/src/features/progressReview/components/DateRangeSelector.tsx:4`) offers three options:
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `tutorFeedback` | Generated by feedback engine | Encouraging message based on metrics |
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `custom` | User-defined | Arbitrary start/end date via date inputs |
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| Preset | Range | Description |
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +```
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +| `30d` | Last 30 days | Monthly review for broader trends |
