[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### AI Prompt Design
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +ProgressReviewReport → ProgressReviewPanel (render)
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +The AI prompt is constructed in `buildAiPrompt()` at `apps/web/src/features/progressReview/services/progressReviewService.ts:282`. It injects structured study data into a prompt that instructs the AI to behave as a personal IELTS tutor.
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Act as an experienced IELTS tutor
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Write in warm, professional tutor tone with "you"
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Be honest but encouraging
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Be specific, reference actual data
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Study period with start/end dates
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Active days, total study time, session count, streak
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Return valid JSON only
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +**User prompt** includes:
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.390Z] [INFO] [stderr] +│                                                    │
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Skill-by-skill progress table
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Explicit instruction to cover all 9 report sections
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### Fallback Mechanism
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +**System prompt** roles:
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Vocabulary status breakdown
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +When the AI call fails (no API key, network error, unparseable response), the system falls back to `buildReportFromData()` at `apps/web/src/features/progressReview/services/progressReviewService.ts:157`. This generates a structured report using local computation:
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Skill trends computed from `ProgressRecord` comparisons
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Study consistency from session date arithmetic
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Recommendations from rule-based heuristics (weak skills, low consistency, unresolved mistakes)
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +- Vocabulary stats from review intervals and repetitions
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### AI Provider Configuration
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +### UI Components
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +Uses the same configuration as the AI Tutor (section 9). If the user has not configured an API key, the feature returns a data-driven report without attempting an AI call.
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +
[2026-07-05T05:29:21.391Z] [INFO] [stderr] +The fallback always produces a valid `ProgressReviewReport` — the feature never shows an empty state after generation.
